  "What is 'cofactor expansion' (also called Laplace expansion)?": "",
  "A technique for expanding the size of a matrix": "",
  "A way to factor matrices into simpler pieces": "",
  "A method that expresses the determinant as a weighted sum of cofactors along any row or column": "",
  "A method for computing eigenvalues": "",
  "Cofactor expansion computes det(A) by summing products of entries and their cofactors along any single row or column: det(A) = sum of a_{ij} * C_{ij}.": "",
